&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Impact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div&gt;- Own recurring Application Security activities for multiple product teams, including secure design reviews, threat modeling, code review, testing validation, and remediation guidance.&lt;/div&gt;
