&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;This is a hands-on AppSec role for someone who can independently own recurring security work across multiple teams. You should be comfortable reviewing architecture and code, validating findings, guiding remediation, and making practical recommendations that balance security, product priorities, and delivery speed.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Impact:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
