&lt;li&gt;Build campaign strategies that incorporate organic social, email, content, field events, webinars, account based plans (1:1 and 1:few) and sales enablement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use AI on a regular basis to help build out programming that aligns with our buyers intent and interests.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Execution &amp;amp; Workflow Management&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead campaign kickoff through completion—coordinating with PMM, content, creative, paid digital, web ops and operations teams.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure all workback schedules, creative requests, and deliverables are structured and tracked effectively in Wrike.&lt;/li&gt;
